{"id":315938,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/香港獨立媒體-谷歌面臨美法院竊聽罪審訊/","date":"2013-09-30T07:20:16Z","modified":"2013-09-30T07:20:16Z","title":"香港獨立媒體 | 谷歌面臨美法院竊聽罪審訊","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n                    <img class=\"imagefield imagefield-field_image\" width=\"500\" height=\"236\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/google%2015th.png?1380520715\" />        </div>\n</p></div>\n</div>\n<p>網絡巨擘谷歌上周十五歲「生日」，特地設計趣緻的「扑糖菓」小遊戲慶祝。不過這生日它過得並不輕鬆，因為美國法院剛裁定谷歌必須面臨一場訴訟。<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://world.yam.com/post.php?id=1011\">谷歌被指控</a>電郵服務非法打開及閱讀Gmail及非Gmail的用戶，涉嫌違反聯邦法院竊聽法。</p>\n<p>原告方指谷歌提供個人化廣告的行為違反了聯邦竊聽法，但谷歌認為用戶同意服務條款已等同接受公司的私隱政策及「閱讀」電郵內容。美國地方法院法官Jucy Koh認為，Gmail及非Gmail用戶並無同意谷歌製作的個人檔案用於廣告用途。谷歌對法庭決定感到失望，又稱自動掃瞄用戶電郵能提供更好的網絡保安及過漏垃圾郵。這意味谷歌想法庭撤回訴訟的願望落空。</p>\n<p>參考報導：<br />\nLos Angeles Times: <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-google-gmail-scanning-lawsuit-judge-ruling-20130926,0,5198528.story?track=rss&#038;utm_source=dlvr.it&#038;utm_medium=twitter&#038;dlvrit=515009\">Google must face suit over scanning of messages in Gmail, judge rules</a><br />\nBloomberg: <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-26/google-must-face-most-claims-in-gmail-wiretap-lawsuit.html\">Google Must Face Most Claims in Gmail Wiretap Lawsuit</a><br />\nAljazeera: <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/09/us-judge-allows-lawsuit-against-google-2013926213729988976.html\">US judge allows lawsuit against Google</a><br />\n網易科技：<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://tech.163.com/13/0927/10/99P7FM22000915BF.html\">谷歌涉嫌违反反窃听法 法院驳回谷歌拒审请求</a></p>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/ms